summary: (gifs by @michaelsheen)  Yknow, seeing michael as aziraphale and also as himself in all these interviews, his humor and playful...
caption:
(gifs by @michaelsheen) 

Yknow, seeing michael as aziraphale and also as himself in all these interviews, his humor and playful lightheartedness absolutely jump off the screen. And it really highlights how subtly he played Bill’s rare and clumsy attempts at playfulness. We see him trying to play along with Gini and it usually falls flat, like when they were role-playing in “Fight” and he’s soooo awkward because this is yet ANOTHER thing his father stole from him; he never felt safe enough to just *play* as a child and that is so fucked up and just like. FEELINGS, man.

summary: The Passion of Port Talbot.  It Has Begun!  BBC WALES Documentary.  This is only a small bit of the 3 day play in Port Talbot,...
caption:
The Passion of Port Talbot. It Has Begun! BBC WALES Documentary.

This is only a small bit of the 3 day play in Port Talbot, but it’s still a really amazing watch. I just scrolled through and landed on 20:00 and it made me well up. Still as beautiful now as it was in 2011. I really recommend watching this documentary to watch some of what was made, the reactions from locals and the process behind it, as well as Sheen’s amazing talent and love creating it.
